类 StudentModule

java.lang.Object
com.study.journey.entity.Module
com.study.journey.entity.StudentModule
public class StudentModule extends Module
The StudentModule class represents a module specific to a student. It extends the Module class, adding a score, finished status, and completion status. copyright : Copyright (c) 2023/5/26

      public StudentModule(String name, String info, String date, String score, int credit, String status)
      Constructs a new StudentModule object with the provided details.
      参数:
      name - The name of the module.
      info - The info of the module.
      date - The date of the module.
      score - The score of the student in the module.
      credit - The credit of the module.
      status - The status of the module (finished or not).
